V0706_01_00_00_0.text:
You know I love you!
And I know you love me much, much more!

V0706_01_00_00_1.text: I won't let the best fans in the world down!

V0706_01_00_01_0.text: Let's kick off this concert with a Rush Duel!

V0706_01_00_02_0.text: Let's Duel to see who's the real King of Duels!

V0706_01_00_03_0.text: Why do I get the feeling you're not Dueling for funsies?

V0706_01_00_04_0.text: Make sure your camera's ready to catch the moment I win!

V0706_01_00_05_0.text: You're the perfect opponent to let me shine on stage!

V0706_01_00_06_0.text: I got some new cards, so my deck's stronger than ever!

V0706_01_00_07_0.text: How about whoever wins gets to be the King of Duels?

V0706_01_00_08_0.text: You seriously think you can defeat me, Romin?

V0706_01_00_09_0.text: Don't forget that I'm still the headliner of this show!

V0706_01_00_10_0.text: It's crazy that a top exec in Goha is a fan of mine!

V0706_01_00_11_0.text:
I have a special guest for this Duel!
The President of Goha!

V0706_01_00_12_0.text: If it's a Duel's you want, it's a Duel you'll get, Asana!

V0706_03_00_00_0.text: Now that we're warmed up, time for the real show to begin!

V0706_03_00_01_0.text: There's no bigger star on stage than me!

V0706_03_00_01_1.text: Keep your eyes on this turn!

V0706_03_00_03_0.text: You don't wanna miss a single moment of this!

V0706_03_00_04_0.text: I may be in trouble, but that just adds to the drama!

V0706_03_00_05_0.text: I can't let you break my rhythm!

V0706_05_00_00_0.text: This jam's not over until I say it is!

V0706_05_00_00_1.text: This draw will bring me to the top!

V0706_06_01_01_0.text: You sure you wanna do that?

V0706_06_01_02_0.text: C'mon, you know that's not gonna work.

V0706_07_09_00_0.text: Did you forget about this card?

V0706_07_09_01_0.text: I'll use the card I Set!

V0706_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0706_11_03_00_0.text: I'll Tribute my monster - with style!

V0706_11_12_00_0.text: I'm gonna Fusion Summon a monster!

V0706_14_00_00_0.text:
Time to play my biggest hits!
Let's battle!

V0706_21_00_00_0.text: You and me - we're just not the same.

V0706_21_00_01_0.text:
I can't end the Duel too quickly.
Gotta give my fans a show!

V0706_21_00_02_0.text: With that, another great turn comes to an end!

V0706_21_00_04_0.text:
Hey now...
You might actually be giving me a scare!

V0706_21_00_05_0.text: There's no way you'll conquer my kingdom!

V0706_28_00_00_0.text: Your Concert King is also gonna be your King of Duels!

V0706_28_00_01_0.text: Only one Duelist can stand above all - and that's me!

V0706_28_00_02_0.text:
Chin up!
You played a great Duel!

V0706_28_00_03_0.text: All I need is a stage to rock out a win!

V0706_28_00_04_0.text: Is this the road to glory that Yuga's always talking about?

V0706_28_00_05_0.text: The King of Duels makes the impossible possible.

V0706_28_00_06_0.text: Just playing to survive isn't gonna get you any fans.

V0706_28_00_07_0.text: I'll become the king of both Dueling and rock 'n roll!

V0706_28_00_08_0.text:
I don't need any Maximum Monsters!
All I need is a mic!

V0706_28_00_09_0.text: Looks like you're the one who needs to catch up to me now.

V0706_28_00_10_0.text:
I know everything about you, Yuga.
Including your tactics.

V0706_28_00_11_0.text: I thought you’d be more of a challenge, but I was wrong.

V0706_28_00_11_1.text: Your Dueling hasn’t gotten better – it’s gotten worse!

V0706_28_00_12_0.text: Your chords aren't as crisp as mine.

V0706_28_00_13_1.text:
By the way...
What's with the mic?
You sing too?

V0706_28_00_14_0.text:
You should learn to loosen up, Asana.
But what do I know.

V0706_28_00_14_1.text:
I’m just the greatest rocker in history.
Not a psychologist.

V0706_28_00_15_0.text: I may have lost, but I'll find my own road to success!

V0706_29_00_00_0.text:
Please stop feeling bad for me.
It's just making it worse.

V0706_29_00_01_0.text: If you'd like, I'm willing to Duel you again.

V0706_29_00_02_0.text: Give a big round of applause for my opponent!

V0706_29_00_03_0.text:
I'm no king.
I'm not even good enough to be a pauper.

V0706_29_00_04_0.text: When things don’t go my way, I just gotta try harder.

V0706_29_00_05_0.text: Not even a psychic can predict your moves, Luke.

V0706_29_00_05_1.text: But I'll take you down next time!

V0706_29_00_06_0.text: You finally had the guts to seize the spotlight, Romin!

V0706_29_00_07_0.text: When Romin's hangry, nothing can stop her.

V0706_29_00_08_0.text:
Otes...
Why did you choose Yuga over me!

V0706_33_00_02_0.text: I'll do whatever it takes to make you my fan!

V0706_33_00_03_0.text: Here's a feast for your ears!

V0706_30_00_00_0.text: Don't you think it's rude to keep a genius like me waiting?

V0706_30_00_01_0.text: I remember all my fans - so why don't I remember you?

V0706_30_00_02_0.text:
That's the right move.
But not sure it's the best move.

V0706_34_00_00_0.text: You think you can back up those words?

V0706_34_00_01_0.text: You shouldn't talk like you know me. Because you don't.

V0706_34_00_03_0.text: I'll make sure you have the Duel of your life!

V0706_34_00_04_0.text: Let the rock flow through ya!

V0706_34_00_05_0.text: Yeah yeah - save those stories for later.

V0706_34_00_06_0.text: By how hard you're trying, you must think you can win.

V0706_34_00_07_0.text: You don't give up. I like that!

V0706_34_00_08_0.text: Let's find out who has the right card to win!

V0706_34_00_09_0.text: I saved this card just for this moment!

V0706_34_00_10_0.text: The road to the throne goes through me!

V0706_34_00_11_0.text:
Once we were friends♪
Capturing bugs and Dueling♪
